      • addMedicament

        public java.lang.String addMedicament​(java.lang.String name,
                                      double dose,
                                      java.lang.String doseCost,
                                      java.lang.String frecuency)
        Description This method allows to add new medicines that were prescription during the hospitalization at the patient stories. pre: The patient clinic story must be not null. post: New medicines were added to the patient clinic story.
        Parameters:
        The - medicine name. This param must be not null.
        The - medicine dose, this param refers to the amount of medicine supplied to the pet each time according the frequence assigned.
        The - medicine cost by each dose. This param could be empty.
        The - frequency of medicine application. This param could be empty.
        Returns:
        A message that indiques if medicine was added to the patient clinic story
